message.body: Actually, I am swinging by to drop something off in 20 if you wanna come over then!
I am gonna try for it. Call me when you get there.
Just wanted to say thanks for meeting me today and helping me out of a jam.
Would tonight be at all a good night to drop off what I borrowed?
I think Sunday eve will work unless I could drop by around midnight on my way home tonight.
Gah, forgot you were coming, had my phone off at rehearsal. So sorry! Will you be up in this area tomorrow 5-6:30 ish by chance? If not I'll have to get it back in December!
...which is not a problem, just a heads up!
I might be through that area just before seven.
